106
00:06:38,100 --> 00:06:39,800
<i> Na to, aby si ním utrel ruky. </ i></i>

107
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,140
<i> Naozaj je v poriadku? </ i></i>

108
00:06:42,940 --> 00:06:44,530
<i> Nemyslím si. </ i></i>

109
00:06:52,950 --> 00:06:55,540
